SUMMARY:Healing Arts 6-Session Workshop
DESCRIPTION:Healing Arts 6-Session Workshop\nFridays\, 10-11:45 AM | Mar. 13\, 20\, 27 & Apr. 3\, 10\, 17\n$25 Members\, $35 Non-Members (all materials included) \nThe Pence’s 6-session Healing Arts workshop uses art as a healing language for those experiencing grief from the loss of a loved one. Through the process of art making\, participants will have opportunities for discussion\, education\, and connecting with peers in a safe and supportive space in the Pence Learning Center under the guidance of facilitators Amy Vidra and Lyndsey Rocca. \nRegistration is required in advance through our website\, and space is limited to the first 8 participants who register. Participants must be 18 or older\, and no art experience is necessary. This program is generously sponsored by Bob & Joanne Andresen. \nRegister (REQUIRED): https://pencegallery.org/education/programs/workshops-and-classes/ \n[Please note that when registering for this program\, you are signing up for all 6 sessions. If you are unable to attend one or more of the sessions\, please let us know in advance.] \nAny questions? Email pencegallery@gmail.com.
URL:https://thedirt.online/event/healing-arts-6-session-workshop/
LOCATION:Pence Gallery\, 212 D Street\, Davis\, CA\, 95616\, United States
CATEGORIES:Art
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://thedirt.online/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Healing_Arts.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Pence Gallery":MAILTO:pencegallery@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
