SUMMARY:Friday Evening at the Winery
DESCRIPTION:🍷✨ Friday Evenings at Great Bear Vineyards ✨🍷\nMarch 13 | 5–8pm\nTicket Includes: First Glass of Wine \nWinter Fridays = cozy vineyard vibes. 🍷❄️ \nWhile live music takes a seasonal pause\, our tasting room is warm\, welcoming\, and ready for your perfect end-of-week unwind. Join us from 5–8pm for relaxed conversation\, delicious estate wines\, and that peaceful vineyard magic you love. \nEnjoy wine by the glass or bottle\, explore a tasting flight\, and grab snacks available for purchase. You’re also welcome to bring your own picnic or favorite takeout and settle in for an easy\, unhurried evening among the vines. \n☀️ Sunny-Day Bonus! \nIf the forecast surprises us with bright blue skies\, we’ll celebrate with a pop-up food truck and live music! Be sure to keep an eye on our social media and website for any sunshine-inspired additions. \nWhether you’re easing into the new year or simply craving a laid-back Friday night out\, winter evenings at Great Bear are all about good wine\, good company\, and a little seasonal magic. \nWe’ll save you a glass
URL:https://thedirt.online/event/friday-evening-at-the-winery-8/
LOCATION:Great Bear Vineyards (Great Bear)\, 24800 County Rd 101A
CATEGORIES:Food & Drink
