SUMMARY:2nd Friday ArtAbout
DESCRIPTION:Check out art receptions\, pop-ups\, open studios\, live music\, and more in Downtown Davis & beyond the evening of March 13. This is a great free event to enjoy with friends and family each month. Participating venues: \nArboretum Art Works\, 17 Arboretum Dr\, Suites G & H | 5:30-7:30 PM\nVisit the working artist collective \nThe Artery\, 207 G St | 6-9 PM\nOn a Clear Day…New Landscape Paintings by Phil Gross \nThe Artist Tree\, 420 F St | 5-9 PM\nThe Artist Tree Dispensary & Art Gallery: Matthew Carden \nDavis Community Church\, 412 C St | 12-1 PM\nLIVE@DCC: 2nd Friday Free Noon Concert \nDavis Craft & Vintage Fair\, E St Plaza | 5-9 PM\nPop-up arts\, crafts\, and vintage sellers + live music (weather permitting) \nJohn Natsoulas Gallery\, 521 1st St | 7-9 PM\nJazz Beat Poetry Night \nThe Local – Dunloe Brewing\, 610 3rd St | 2-10 PM\n2025 Drawing Club Showcase \nLogos Books\, 513 2nd St | 5:30-7:30 PM\nFutaba Wood & Walker Mason: Living Together in Harmony \nThe Paint Chip\, 217 F St | 6-8:30 PM\nAmy McElwain: The Paper Menagerie \nPence Gallery\, 212 D St | 6-9 PM\nManuel Fernando Rios: When They Reminisce Over You\nAssorted Flavors: Pence Member Exhibit\nBarbara Prodaniuk: Myths in Mud\nLoraine Watson-Fox: Small Wonders \nThird Space Art Collective\, 17 Arboretum Dr\, Unit C | 5-8 PM\nFrowns and Foolery: Of The Queer Community \n[OFF-MAP EVENTS] \nDavis Arts Center\, 1919 F St | 5-7 PM\nFamily Open Studio \n– \nThe ArtAbout is coordinated by the Pence Gallery and sponsored by Signature Sponsor Willowgrove and the Davis Downtown Business Association. To support this free community offering as a sponsor\, please visit https://pencegallery.org/events/artabout/. \nImages:\nAmy McElwain (The Paint Chip)\nJonah Skow (The Local – Dunloe Brewing)\nWalker Mason (Logos Books)\nMichelle Martin\, LuAnn Higgs\, Robin Houston (Davis Community Church)
URL:https://thedirt.online/event/2nd-friday-artabout-2/
LOCATION:Downtown Davis Various Locations
CATEGORIES:Art,Bring the Kids,Community
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://thedirt.online/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/2nd-Friday-4x5-1.png
ORGANIZER;CN="Pence Gallery":MAILTO:pencegallery@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
