UID:10075444-1773423000-1773430200@thedirt.online
SUMMARY:2nd Friday ArtAbout reception: Futaba Wood & Walker Mason
DESCRIPTION:Living Together in Harmony\nFutaba Wood: watercolor\, acrylic\nWalker Mason: photography\nMarch 3 to March 28\n2nd Friday ArtAbout Reception: March 13\, 5:30 p.m. to 7:30 p.m.\nLogos Books\, 513 Second Street\, Davis\, CA\, 95616 \nFrom Futaba Wood:\nLife can be chaotic\, heartbreaking and enigmatic. Life can also be vibrant\, joyous and transformative. It’s far from simple\, but there is a certain kind of harmony to it all. That harmony is sometimes most apparent when we realize that\, despite our differences\, we are all quite similar. In nature\, many kinds of animals live side by side. Can humans – divided by race\, gender\, and background – do the same in this world? Or is this hope merely a fragile dream? These thoughts played an important role in our approach to this show. The two of us come from different backgrounds and generations and we each employ distinct mediums to create our art. In this show we wanted to celebrate our individual perspectives while simultaneously highlighting our shared appreciation for the natural world and the intrinsic harmony of life. Email: dfwood@comcast.net \nFrom Walker Mason:\nI’ve experimented with a number of different art forms\, but photography is where my heart truly lies. For me the true beauty of photography is that I can create art everywhere I go. I enjoy capturing the things I encounter in my daily life. While studying at the University of Hawai’i I became enthralled with the darkroom process. My time there reshaped the way I work. Today\, I strive to honor the tradition of analog photography and share my passion with others. Instagram @heron_photographic
URL:https://thedirt.online/event/2nd-friday-artabout-reception-futaba-wood-walker-mason/
LOCATION:Logos Books\, 513 2nd Street\, Davis\, CA\, 95616\, United States
CATEGORIES:Art,Bring the Kids,Community
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://thedirt.online/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/F-Wood-2-scaled.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Davis Downtown":MAILTO:info@davisdowntown.com
GEO:38.5433266;-121.7415642
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Logos Books 513 2nd Street Davis CA 95616 United States;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=513 2nd Street:geo:-121.7415642,38.5433266
END:VEVENT
