DESCRIPTION:Sacred Space Evening with Singing Bowls by Brenda Mohr\nFriday\, March 13\, 6- 6:30 pm\nDCC Sanctuary (4th street between C & D)\nFree! \nCome relax your mind and enjoy a time of gentle meditation in the beautiful DCC Sanctuary. \nAfterwards\, enjoy tea and biscotti offered by Purple Tree Cafe in the entry hall. \nThis event is in conjunction with 2nd Friday ArtAbout – so you may wish to stroll downtown afterwards for dinner and then peruse the various art events happening!
