SUMMARY:2nd Friday ArtAbout at the Pence Gallery
DESCRIPTION:Join us at the Pence Gallery for our 2nd Friday ArtAbout reception on March 13\, 6-9 PM. Enjoy browsing multiple art exhibits\, complimentary wine by Matchbook Wines\, and an art-themed scavenger hunt. Also\, view special floral arrangements within the exhibits by the Davis Flower Arrangers. Free admission! \nManuel Fernando Rios: When They Reminisce Over You | Feb. 7 – Mar. 29\nThe artist’s work explores his Chicano heritage\, as well as his family’s history and experiences. Blurring the line between naturalism and abstraction\, he embraces the use of complex design patterns and photography to make a powerful statement. \nAssorted Flavors: Pence Member Exhibit | Mar. 13 – Apr. 16\nOur 2nd annual non-juried exhibit celebrates the creativity and talent of our organization’s supporters\, showcasing work in different media by 40 Pence Members. \nBarbara Prodaniuk: Myths in Mud | Mar. 13 – Apr. 26\nThe ceramic artist’s work is inspired by the forest\, meadows\, and waterways surrounding the Truckee area. She explores the stories carried by the creatures and artifacts found in these environments through layered surfaces\, organic textures\, and sculpted imagery. \nLoraine Watson-Fox: Small Wonders | Mar. 6 – Mar. 29\nThe artist employs mixed-media including collage\, text\, thread and textural elements to enhance her use of more traditional paint media. Her work is on display along the stairway. \nDavis Flower Arrangers: Art in Bloom | Mar. 13 – Mar. 15\nIn a special collaboration\, the Davis Flower Arrangers have put together creative floral arrangements to be paired with specific artworks on view at the Pence. \nScavenger Hunt: Join us for a fun\, art-themed scavenger hunt at the Pence during the 2nd Friday ArtAbout. Complete all of the clues by exploring our exhibits for the chance to win a special prize. \n— \nVisit the Pence and other venues in Downtown Davis for the 2nd Friday ArtAbout artwalk. We will have printed ArtAbout guides available that week. Follow the ArtAbout’s Facebook page for more information: https://www.facebook.com/davisartabout. \nImages:\nManuel Fernando Rios\, “Jose as Huitzilopochtli”\nBarbara Prodaniuk\, “Raven Vase”\nLoraine Watson-Fox\, “156”\nDavis Flower Arrangement (past event)
URL:https://thedirt.online/event/2nd-friday-artabout-at-the-pence-gallery-3/
LOCATION:Pence Gallery\, 212 D Street\, Davis\, CA\, 95616\, United States
CATEGORIES:Art,Community
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://thedirt.online/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Pence-Reception-4x5-1.png
ORGANIZER;CN="Pence Gallery":MAILTO:pencegallery@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
